ra Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|12=draft|12=draft}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|ja|村上藩|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|ja|姫路藩|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Harima Province|ja|播磨国|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1675|}}). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1749|}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Gentaemon|ja|丸山権太左衛門|12=draft|12=draft}}, a 3rd-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1713|}}).
