== Events == * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1087|}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – {{ill|Gosannen no Eki|ja|後三年の役|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ended. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1871|}} {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}） – The {{ill|Haihan Chiken|ja|廃藩置県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} reform led to the birth of {{ill|Saitama Prefecture|ja|埼玉県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * 明治4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1871, 12月25日) – By the same reform, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was also established.
== Births == * {{ill|Chōkan|ja|長寛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1164|}} {{ill|December 28|ja|12月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Rokujō|ja|六条天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 79th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1176|}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1630|}} {{ill|December 17|ja|12月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kaihara Ekken|ja|貝原益軒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a {{ill|Ru (Confucian scholar)|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|1714|}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|735|}} {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Prince Sotoneri|ja|舎人親王|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the fifth prince of {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|天武天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, who led the editing of the {{ill|Nihon Shoki|ja|日本書紀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died {{ill|676|}}). * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1087|}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kiyohara Iehiro|ja|清原家衡|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a warrior of the Heian period. * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉承|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1107|}} {{ill|December 29|ja|12月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Kimoto|ja|藤原公実|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a kugyō and {{ill|Waka poet|ja|歌人|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Heian period (born {{ill|1053|}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1603|}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗章|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a practitioner of {{ill|Kenjutsu|ja|剣術|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of the Azuchi–Momoyama period (born {{ill|1566|}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1627|}} {{ill|December 21|ja|12月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠利|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Tanaka Domain|ja|田中藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Suruga Province|ja|駿河国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Kawagoe Domain|ja|川越藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1559|}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1726|}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|ja|村上藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|ja|姫路藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Harima Province|ja|播磨国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born {{ill|1675|}}). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|