ian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1627||qq=}} {{ill|December 21|ja|12月21日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠利|qq=}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Tanaka Domain|ja|田中藩|qq=}} in {{ill|Suruga Province|ja|駿河国|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Kawagoe Domain|ja|川越藩|qq=}} in {{ill|Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国|qq=}} (born {{ill|1559||qq=}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1726||qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|qq=}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|ja|村上藩|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|ja|姫路藩|qq=}} in {{ill|Harima Province|ja|播磨国|qq=}} (born {{ill|1675||qq=}}). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1749||qq=}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Gentaemon|ja|丸山権太左衛門|qq=}}, a 3rd-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=}} (born {{ill|1713||qq=}}).
