{{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 14''' is the 14th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1087||qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=}}） – {{ill|Gosannen no Eki|ja|後三年の役|qq=}} ended. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} {{ill|1871||qq=}} {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|qq=}}） – The {{ill|Haihan Chiken|ja|廃藩置県|qq=}} reform led to the birth of {{ill|Saitama Prefecture|ja|埼玉県|qq=}}. * 明治4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} 1871, 12月25日) – By the same reform, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|qq=}} was also established.
