{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月十四|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 14일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 14''' is the 14th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Shakkō|ja|赤口|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shakkō|qq=}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanchi|qq=}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1087|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1087|qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 11|qq=}}） – {{ill|Gosannen no Eki|ja|後三年の役|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gosannen no Eki|qq=}} ended. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1871|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}} {{ill|December 25|ja|12月25日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 25|qq=}}） – The {{ill|Haihan Chiken|ja|廃藩置県|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Haihan Chiken|qq=}} reform led to the birth of {{ill|Saitama Prefecture|ja|埼玉県|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Saitama Prefecture|qq=}}. * 明治4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} 1871, 12月25日) – By the same reform, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōita Prefecture|qq=}} was also established.
== Births == * {{ill|Chōkan|ja|長寛|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chōkan|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1164|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1164|qq=}} {{ill|December 28|ja|12月28日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 28|qq=}}) – {{ill|Emperor Rokujō|ja|六条天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Rokujō|qq=}}, the 79th {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor of Japan|qq=}} (died {{ill|1176|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1176|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1630|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1630|qq=}} {{ill|December 17|ja|12月17日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 17|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kaihara Ekken|ja|貝原益軒|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kaihara Ekken|qq=}}, a {{ill|Ru (Confucian scholar)|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died {{ill|1714|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1714|qq=}}).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|735|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/735|qq=}} {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Prince Sotoneri|ja|舎人親王|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Sotoneri|qq=}}, the fifth prince of {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|天武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Tenmu|qq=}}, who led the editing of the {{ill|Nihon Shoki|ja|日本書紀|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nihon Shoki|qq=}} (died {{ill|676|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/676|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanchi|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1087|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1087|qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 11|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kiyohara Iehiro|ja|清原家衡|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyohara Iehiro|qq=}}, a warrior of the Heian period. * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉承|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashō|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1107|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1107|qq=}} {{ill|December 29|ja|12月29日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Kimoto|ja|藤原公実|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Kimoto|qq=}}, a kugyō and {{ill|Waka poet|ja|歌人|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Waka poet|qq=}} of the Heian period (born {{ill|1053|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1053|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1603|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1603|qq=}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 16|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗章|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagyū Munenori|qq=}}, a practitioner of {{ill|Kenjutsu|ja|剣術|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenjutsu|qq=}} of the Azuchi–Momoyama period (born {{ill|1566|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1566|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1627|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1627|qq=}} {{ill|December 21|ja|12月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 21|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠利|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakai Tadayoshi|qq=}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Tanaka Domain|ja|田中藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanaka Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Suruga Province|ja|駿河国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suruga Province|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Kawagoe Domain|ja|川越藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawagoe Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Musashi Province|qq=}} (born {{ill|1559|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1559|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1726|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1726|qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakakibara Masakuni|qq=}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|ja|村上藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Murakami Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|ja|姫路藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Himeji Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Harima Province|ja|播磨国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Harima Province|qq=}} (born {{ill|1675|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1675|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannen|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1749|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1749|qq=}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 23|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Gentaemon|ja|丸山権太左衛門|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maruyama Gentaemon|qq=}}, a 3rd-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|qq=}} (born {{ill|1713|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1713|qq=}}).
