== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenpyō|ja|天平|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|735|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/735|qq=}} {{ill|December 2|ja|12月2日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 2|qq=}}) – {{ill|Prince Sotoneri|ja|舎人親王|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prince Sotoneri|qq=}}, the fifth prince of {{ill|Emperor Tenmu|ja|天武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Tenmu|qq=}}, who led the editing of the {{ill|Nihon Shoki|ja|日本書紀|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nihon Shoki|qq=}} (died {{ill|676|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/676|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kanchi|ja|寛治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanchi|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1087|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1087|qq=}} {{ill|December 11|ja|12月11日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 11|qq=}}) – {{ill|Kiyohara Iehiro|ja|清原家衡|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kiyohara Iehiro|qq=}}, a warrior of the Heian period. * {{ill|Kashō|ja|嘉承|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashō|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1107|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1107|qq=}} {{ill|December 29|ja|12月29日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Kimoto|ja|藤原公実|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Kimoto|qq=}}, a kugyō and {{ill|Waka poet|ja|歌人|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Waka poet|qq=}} of the Heian period (born {{ill|1053|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1053|qq=}}). * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 8th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1603|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1603|qq=}} {{ill|December 16|ja|12月16日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 16|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗章|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagyū Munenori|qq=}}, a practitioner of {{ill|Kenjutsu|ja|剣術|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kenjutsu|qq=}} of the Azuchi–Momoyama period (born {{ill|1566|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1566|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'ei|qq=}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1627|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1627|qq=}} {{ill|December 21|ja|12月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 21|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadayoshi|ja|酒井忠利|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakai Tadayoshi|qq=}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Tanaka Domain|ja|田中藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tanaka Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Suruga Province|ja|駿河国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suruga Province|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Kawagoe Domain|ja|川越藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawagoe Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Musashi Province|ja|武蔵国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Musashi Province|qq=}} (born {{ill|1559|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1559|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyōhō|qq=}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1726|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1726|qq=}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 7|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakakibara Masakuni|qq=}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|ja|村上藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Murakami Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|ja|越後国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Echigo Province|qq=}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|ja|姫路藩|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Himeji Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Harima Province|ja|播磨国|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Harima Province|qq=}} (born {{ill|1675|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1675|qq=}}). * {{ill|Kannen|ja|寛延|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannen|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1749|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1749|qq=}} {{ill|December 23|ja|12月23日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 23|qq=}}) – {{ill|Maruyama Gentaemon|ja|丸山権太左衛門|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Maruyama Gentaemon|qq=}}, a 3rd-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|qq=}} (born {{ill|1713|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1713|qq=}}).
