== Births == * [[:en:Chōkan|Chōkan]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1164|1164]] [[:en:December 28|December 28]]) – [[:en:Emperor Rokujō|Emperor Rokujō]], the 79th [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor of Japan]] (died [[:en:1176|1176]]). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 7th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1630|1630]] [[:en:December 17|December 17]]) – [[:en:Kaibara Ekken|Kaihara Ekken]], a {{ill|Ru (Confucian scholar)|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru (Confucian scholar)|qq=}} (died [[:en:1714|1714]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Tenpyō|Tenpyō]] 7th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:735|735]] [[:en:December 2|December 2]]) – [[:en:Prince Toneri|Prince Sotoneri]], the fifth prince of [[:en:Emperor Tenmu|Emperor Tenmu]], who led the editing of the [[:en:Nihon Shoki|Nihon Shoki]] (died [[:en:676|676]]). * [[:en:Kanji (era)|Kanchi]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1087|1087]] [[:en:December 11|December 11]]) – [[:en:Kiyohara no Iehira|Kiyohara Iehiro]], a warrior of the Heian period. * [[:en:Kajō|Kashō]] 2nd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1107|1107]] [[:en:December 29|December 29]]) – {{ill|Fujiwara no Kimoto|ja|藤原公実|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fujiwara no Kimoto|qq=}}, a kugyō and {{ill|Waka poet|ja|歌人|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Waka poet|qq=}} of the Heian period (born [[:en:1053|1053]]). * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 8th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1603|1603]] [[:en:December 16|December 16]]) – {{ill|Yagyū Munenori|ja|柳生宗章|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yagyū Munenori|qq=}}, a practitioner of [[:en:Kenjutsu|Kenjutsu]] of the Azuchi–Momoyama period (born [[:en:1566|1566]]). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1627|1627]] [[:en:December 21|December 21]]) – [[:en:Sakai Tadatoshi|Sakai Tadayoshi]], the first lord of the [[:en:Tanaka Domain|Tanaka Domain]] in [[:en:Suruga Province|Suruga Province]], and the first lord of the [[:en:Kawagoe Domain|Kawagoe Domain]] in [[:en:Musashi Province|Musashi Province]] (born [[:en:1559|1559]]). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1726|1726]] [[:en:December 7|December 7]]) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakakibara Masakuni|qq=}}, the second lord of the [[:en:Murakami Domain|Murakami Domain]] in [[:en:Echigo Province|Echigo Province]], and the first lord of the [[:en:Himeji Domain|Himeji Domain]] in [[:en:Harima Province|Harima Province]] (born [[:en:1675|1675]]). * [[:en:Kan'en|Kannen]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1749|1749]] [[:en:December 23|December 23]]) – [[:en:Maruyama Gondazaemon|Maruyama Gentaemon]], a 3rd-generation {{ill|Yokozuna|ja|横綱|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokozuna|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} (born [[:en:1713|1713]]).
