nori|1=Yagyū Muneaki|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11534528}}, a practitioner of {{ill|Kenjutsu|en|Kenjutsu|WD=Q249608|lt=Kenjutsu|1=Kenjutsu}} of the Azuchi–Momoyama period (born {{ill|1566|en|1566|WD=Q6638|lt=1566|1=1566}}). * {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|WD=Q1192913|lt=Kan'ei|1=Kan'ei}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1627|en|1627|WD=Q6833|lt=1627|1=1627}} {{ill|December 21|en|December 21|WD=Q2603|lt=December 21|1=December 21}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadatoshi|en|Sakai Tadatoshi|WD=Q11644106|lt=Sakai Tadayoshi|1=Sakai Tadatoshi}}, the first lord of the {{ill|Tanaka Domain|en|Tanaka Domain|WD=Q420800|lt=Tanaka Domain|1=Tanaka Domain}} in {{ill|Suruga Province|en|Suruga Province|WD=Q864170|lt=Suruga Province|1=Suruga Province}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Kawagoe Domain|en|Kawagoe Domain|WD=Q3034465|lt=Kawagoe Domain|1=Kawagoe Domain}} in {{ill|Musashi Province|en|Musashi Province|WD=Q907398|lt=Musashi Province|1=Musashi Province}} (born {{ill|1559|en|1559|WD=Q6609|lt=1559|1=1559}}). * {{ill|Kyōhō|en|Kyōhō|WD=Q1145048|lt=Kyōhō|1=Kyōhō}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1726|en|1726|WD=Q6936|lt=1726|1=1726}} {{ill|December 7|en|December 7|WD=Q2299|lt=December 7|1=December 7}}) – {{ill|Sakakibara Masakuni|ja|榊原政邦|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sakakibara Masakuni|1=Sakakibara Masakuni|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11541708}}, the second lord of the {{ill|Murakami Domain|en|Murakami Domain|WD=Q849483|lt=Murakami Domain|1=Murakami Domain}} in {{ill|Echigo Province|en|Echigo Province|WD=Q666514|lt=Echigo Province|1=Echigo Province}}, and the first lord of the {{ill|Himeji Domain|en|Himeji Domain|WD=Q1062190|lt=Himeji Domain|1=Himeji Domain}} in {{ill|Harima Province|en|Harima Province|WD=Q1047523|lt=Harima Province|1=Harima Province}} (born {{ill|1675|en|1675|WD=Q7624|lt=1675|1=1675}}